%       defined, we try to extract the slot number.
%\changes{v1.7}{2005/02/27}{test whether \cs{}\meta{encoding}\cs{}\meta{...} is defined}
%\changes{v1.8}{2005/04/04}{test whether \cs{}\meta{encoding}\cs{}\meta{...} is defined
